# Reddit API Configuration
# IMPORTANT: These must be set as Supabase secrets, not just in .env
# Go to your Supabase project dashboard > Settings > Edge Functions > Secrets
# and add these as secrets:
REDDIT_USERNAME=your-reddit-username
REDDIT_PASSWORD=your-reddit-password
REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your-reddit-client-id
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your-reddit-client-secret

# Reddit Setup Instructions:
# 1. Create a Reddit app at https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps/
# 2. Choose "script" as the app type
# 3. Use http://localhost:8080 as the redirect URI
# 4. Copy the client ID (under the app name) and client secret
# 5. Make sure your Reddit account does NOT have 2FA enabled
# 6. Set these values as Supabase secrets (not just in .env)

